# ELECTRA Frontend — Build Walkthrough

## Summary

Built a complete, production-ready React 19 + TypeScript frontend for the ELECTRA TPS Management Dashboard. The app comprises **50+ files** across 7 pages, 20+ custom UI components, bilingual support, and full API integration.

## Architecture

```mermaid
graph TD
    A["main.tsx"] --> B["QueryClientProvider"]
    B --> C["ToastProvider"]
    C --> D["RouterProvider"]
    D --> E{"Auth Guard"}
    E -->|Authenticated| F["DashboardLayout"]
    E -->|Unauthenticated| G["LoginPage"]
    F --> H["Sidebar + Header"]
    H --> I["Page Outlet"]
    I --> J["Dashboard"]
    I --> K["TPS Management"]
    I --> L["Map View"]
    I --> M["Officers"]
    I --> N["Assignments"]
    I --> O["Vote Results"]
```

