### Pages (7)
| Page | Key Features |
|---|---|
| [Login](file:///c:/Experience/projects/tps-management/tps-management-frontend/src/pages/login.tsx) | Split layout, PAN branding gradient, Zod form validation |
| [Dashboard](file:///c:/Experience/projects/tps-management/tps-management-frontend/src/pages/dashboard.tsx) | 4 stat cards, Recharts bar + donut chart, quick actions |
| [TPS Management](file:///c:/Experience/projects/tps-management/tps-management-frontend/src/pages/polling-station-management.tsx) | Filterable table, CRUD modals, import, pagination |
| [Map View](file:///c:/Experience/projects/tps-management/tps-management-frontend/src/pages/map-view.tsx) | Leaflet map, clustered markers, color by status, filter sidebar |
| [Officers](file:///c:/Experience/projects/tps-management/tps-management-frontend/src/pages/officers.tsx) | Table, role/district filters, add/edit form modal |
| [Assignments](file:///c:/Experience/projects/tps-management/tps-management-frontend/src/pages/assignments.tsx) | Table with confirm action, status filter, create form |
| [Vote Results](file:///c:/Experience/projects/tps-management/tps-management-frontend/src/pages/vote-results.tsx) | Aggregated + detailed views, bar chart, district table |

