## Verification

- ✅ Vite dev server runs on `http://localhost:5174` without compilation errors
- ✅ CSS import order fixed (Google Fonts before Tailwind)
- ✅ Login page renders correctly in browser
- ✅ HMR working for live changes
- ✅ All routes lazy-loaded with Suspense fallback
